    "description": "Authoritative cross-session reference document describing how all modules of the ADA Reasonable Accommodation Decision Engine connect. Defines module inventory, component outputs, cross-module dependencies, wrapper behavior, and architectural design decisions. Intended for use as a build session reference file.",
